attribute.description:
Sets the input coordinate type: 

- "aed": azimuth, Elevation, distance (spherical coordinates); 

- "xyz": cartesian coordinates; 

- "azr": azimuth, Z, axial radius (cylindrical coordinates). 

Azimuth is considered 0 at the front, and increases clockwise.
X is the left-right axis (positive to the right) while Y is front-back axis (positive to the front).
